        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Real Emergencies Act</strong></p> <p>This bill denies the President authority to declare a national emergency, an emergency or major disaster, or a public health emergency on the premise of climate change.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
